pr_body:
PR for issue #325

Added support for timezone param in api_occurrences() function to make possible api calls with timezone param, for example:
```
$('#calendar').fullCalendar({
    events: '/schedule/api/occurrences?calendar_slug=test&timezone=America/Chicago'
});

```
Param timezone is described in https://fullcalendar.io/docs/timezone/timezone/

Allow "pivot_ui" to receive some config. params for the Javascript widget, for example:

df = pd.DataFrame({"a":["col","alto","ancho","bla"],"b":[2,3,4,5],"c":[6,2,6,8]});
pivot_ui(df, rows=["a"],cols=["b"],vals=["c"],aggregatorName="Sum",rendererName = "Heatmap")

